 -----Original Message-----
From:  GISB1@aol.com@ENRON 
[mailto:IMCEANOTES-GISB1+40aol+2Ecom+40ENRON@ENRON.com] 
Sent: Tuesday, May 29, 2001 9:50 PM
To: Gisb@aol.com; GISB4@aol.com
Subject: GISB Member Ratification Ballot

Dear GISB Members,

In .pdf format bookmarked, please find the attached ballot to record your
vote on the ratification of a recommendation modifying two GISB standards.
The recommendation was adopted by the Executive Committee (EC) on May 29,
2001.  To record your vote, please fill out page two of this communication
and either email (gisb@aol.com) or fax it (713-356-0067) to our office by
June 15.  The shortened period for ratification was approved by the EC on May
29.  Should the recommendation be ratified, it will be included in the
publication of version 1.5 of the standards.

The EC voting record and discussion of this item is contained within the EC
minutes of May 29, 2001.  The EC minutes can be found on the GISB home page
(www.gisb.org), as can the request, recommendation, and related subcommittee
and task force minutes.  Transcripts of the EC meeting where this
recommendation was discussed can be ordered by calling the GISB office --
713-356-0060.

