PWC to provide ENE a template for evaluating each of the synergies we 
mutually agreed need focusing on now. (1/24)
PWC to provide ENE a similar template for the various growth prospects 
discussed (1/24)
Initial follow up meeting (same participants from ENE) on Monday, 1/24 to 
begin rationalizing the data and quantifying the numbers.
Rough draft of study due before 2/1 meeting.
Final draft prior to 2/4 meeting.

