From MAILER-DAEMON Mon Apr 18 14:23:29 2022
Message-ID: <7832235.1075844941161.JavaMail.evans@thyme>
Date: Mon, 24 Jul 2000 00:15:00 -0700 (PDT)
From: ron.m.mucci@williams.com
To: shorton@enron.com
Subject: FW: Strawman
Mime-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=us-ascii
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit
X-From: "Mucci, Ron M" <Ron.M.Mucci@Williams.com>
X-To: shorton@enron.com
